data.name: Yuiro, the Luxuriant
data.notes: "Yuiro, the Luxuriant" will appear in the lone bush when its fellow Blatta have all been killed on top of a tall column of stone at the north end of Qing Long Glade in Noctilum (just below the twin hammers bridge that has a noticeable gap in it). The Blatta will take several seconds to appear and has a short load/despawn distance so land the Skell and be patient.
